{"header":"<h1>Module type <code><span>Memory_sig.OFFSET_AND_MAKE_BLOCK</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":true,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Domains","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Memory_sig","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"OFFSET_AND_MAKE_BLOCK","href":"#","kind":"module-type"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>The idea is to match a <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/index.html\"><code>BLOCK</code></a> with the representation of an <a href=\"../module-type-OFFSET/index.html\"><code>OFFSET</code></a> within that <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/index.html\"><code>BLOCK</code></a>. But we delay the creation of the Block using a <a href=\"Make_Block/index.html\" title=\"OFFSET_AND_MAKE_BLOCK.Make_Block\"><code>Make_Block</code></a> functor, as the <a href=\"../module-type-OFFSET/index.html\"><code>OFFSET</code></a> can be used to create the <a href=\"../module-type-VALUE/index.html\"><code>VALUE</code></a> that the <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/index.html\"><code>BLOCK</code></a> contains.</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Scalar\"><a href=\"#module-Scalar\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a></span><span> : <a href=\"../../Sig/module-type-BASE/index.html\">Sig.BASE</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Offset\"><a href=\"#module-Offset\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Offset/index.html\">Offset</a></span><span> : <a href=\"../module-type-OFFSET/index.html\">OFFSET</a> <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../module-type-OFFSET/Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a> = <a href=\"Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a></span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Make_Block\"><a href=\"#module-Make_Block\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Make_Block/index.html\">Make_Block</a></span><span>\u000A  (<a href=\"Make_Block/argument-1-Value/index.html\">Value</a> : <a href=\"../module-type-VALUE/index.html\">VALUE</a> <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../module-type-VALUE/Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a> = <a href=\"Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a></span>) : \u000A  <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/index.html\">BLOCK</a>\u000A    <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a> = <a href=\"Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a></span>\u000A     <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/Value/index.html\">Value</a> = <a href=\"Make_Block/argument-1-Value/index.html\">Value</a></span>\u000A     <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/Offset/index.html\">Offset</a> = <a href=\"Offset/index.html\">Offset</a></span>\u000A     <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"../module-type-BLOCK/index.html#type-boolean\">boolean</a> = <a href=\"Make_Block/argument-1-Value/index.html#type-boolean\">Value.boolean</a></span></span></code></div></div>"}